trans-unit.source: Each element of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601> collection is a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601>.

The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601> contains a value, a reference to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601> that it belongs to, a reference to the next node, and a reference to the previous node.
Specifies the element type of the linked list.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1"></xref> class, containing the specified value.

The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601.List%2A>, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601.Next%2A>, and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601.Previous%2A> properties are set to `null`.
The value to contain in the <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1"></xref>.
Gets the <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1"></xref> that the <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1"></xref> belongs to.

A reference to the <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1"></xref> that the <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1"></xref> belongs to, or `null` if the <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1"></xref> is not linked.
Gets the next node in the <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1"></xref>.

A reference to the next node in the <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1"></xref>, or `null` if the current node is the last element (<xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1.Last"></xref>) of the <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1"></xref>.
Gets the previous node in the <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1"></xref>.

A reference to the previous node in the <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1"></xref>, or `null` if the current node is the first element (<xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1.First"></xref>) of the <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1"></xref>.
Gets the value contained in the node.
This property is set in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601.%23ctor%2A>.
The value contained in the node.
